serializableData.oldContent: HOW TO PLAY
Click the             button to open the bet menu. Select the bet you want to use in the game by adjusting values using the           and           buttons.
Press the SPIN button to play.
MENU
opens the menu that contains the settings which affect the way the game is being played.
takes you to the casino lobby
helps reduce the battery consumption of the game and can help to prevent the device from becoming warm during longer play sessions
toggles sound and music on and off
opens the game history page
opens the Information page

CREDIT and BET labels show the current balance and current total bet.
Click on the labels to switch between coins view and cash view.
MENU
starts the game
Hold on the
button to open the Autoplay menu
INFORMATION SCREEN
Drag pages up and down to scroll between information pages
closes the information screen
BET MENU
The bet menu shows the number of lines available in the game, and the current total bet in both coins and cash.
Use the          and          buttons in the COINS PER LINE and COIN VALUE fields to change the values.
AUTOPLAY
Click on the buttons showing the number of possible auto-spins to start Autoplay
SKIP SCREENS option auto-skips the feature introduction and end screens after a short period of time
STOP AUTOPLAY
ON ANY WIN  whenever you win something, the Autoplay function stops
IF FEATURE IS WON  whenever a feature like bonus game or free spins is won, Autoplay will stop
IF SINGLE WIN EXCEEDS  whenever a single win is above the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
IF CASH INCREASES BY  whenever your current balance is above the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
IF CASH DECREASES BY  whenever your current balance is below the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
START AUTOPLAY  starts the Autoplay function

GAME RULES
This symbol is WILD and substitutes for all symbols except for
WILD symbol is present on all reels.
The BONUS symbol is present on reels 2, 3, and 4.
Hit 3x           to trigger the FREE SPINS FEATURE.
SUPER RESPIN RULES
Hit two or more full stacks of           anywhere on the reels to trigger the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE.
When the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE is triggered the game pays for regular winning combinations, after which only the full stacks of           remain on the reels.
The round starts with 3 respins. During the round, only            symbols are spinning. Every time a new           hits it remains on the reels and one more respin is awarded.
When no more respins are left, all win combinations with           are added together and paid.

If at the end of the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE 14            symbols are on screen, the 
MAJOR JACKPOT is awarded instead of win lines. The MAJOR JACKPOT is fixed at 375x total bet.

If during the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE 15           hit, the feature ends immediately and the 
GRAND JACKPOT is awarded instead of win lines. The GRAND JACKPOT is fixed at 500x total bet.
If the FREE SPINS FEATURE has been awarded by the same spin that awarded the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE, the FREE SPINS FEATURE will be played after the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE is over.
FREE SPINS RULES
The BONUS symbol is present on reels 2, 3, and 4.
Hit 3x           to trigger the FREE SPINS FEATURE.
User is awarded 10 free spins.

During the FREE SPINS ROUND, all           symbols are WILD and substitute for all symbols.
         pays with the wild paytable
Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
The SUPER RESPIN FEATURE cannot be triggered during the FREE SPINS ROUND.           symbol is not present on the reels during the FREE SPINS ROUND and the feature cannot be retriggered.
VOLATILITY
Medium volatility games pay out steadily and the range of pays varies from low to very high
GAME RULES

All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines.
Free Spins win is added to the payline win.
All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
Only the highest win is paid per line.
The theoretical RTP of this game is {0}%
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

PRAVILA IGRE
Ovaj je simbol WILD i mijenja sve simbole osim simbola
Simbol WILD postoji na svim rolama.
Simbol BONUS pojavljuje se na 2., 3. i 4. roli.

Ako dobijete 3x        , pokree se ZNAAJKA BESPLATNIH
VRTNJI.
PRAVILA SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE

Pogodite dva ili vie puna stoga simbola          bilo gdje na rolama kako biste pokrenuli
ZNAAJKU SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE.

Kada se pokrene ZNAAJKA SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE, igra isplauje za uobiajene dobitne
 kombinacije nakon ega samo potpuno naslagani simboli        ostaju na rolama.

Krug poinje s 3 ponovne vrtnje. U krugu se samo puni stogovi
simbola        Svaki put kada pogodite novi simbol        , on ostaje na
roli i dodjeljuje vam se dodatna ponovna vrtnja
Kada vie nema ponovnih vrtnji, sve dobitne kombinacije sa simbolom        zbrajaju se i isplauju.

Ako na kraju ZNAAJKE SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE 14 simbola        bude na zaslonu, 
dodjeljuje se VELIKI JACKPOT umjesto dobitnih linija. VELIKI JACKPOT ima fiksni iznos od 375x ukupni ulog.

Ako u ZNAAJCI SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE dobijete 15 simbola        , znaajka se odmah prekida 
 i dodjeljuje se GRAND JACKPOT umjesto dobitnih linija. GRAND JACKPOT ima fiksni iznos od 500x ukupni ulog.

Ako je dodijeljena ZNAAJKA BESPLATNIH VRTNJI u istoj vrtnji u kojoj je dodijeljena ZNAAJKA SUPER
PONOVNE VRTNJE, ZNAAJKA BESPLATNIH VRTNJI igra se nakon ZNAAJKE SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE.
PRAVILA ZA BESPLATNE VRTNJE
Simbol BONUS pojavljuje se na 2., 3. i 4. roli.
Ako dobijete 3x        , pokree se ZNAAJKA BESPLATNIH VRTNJI.
Korisnik dobiva 10 besplatnih vrtnji.

U KRUGU BESPLATNIH VRTNJI, svi su simboli        WILD i mijenjaju sve druge simbole.
        donosi dobitak u skladu s tablicom dobitaka za wild.
Posebne role u igri su u znaajci besplatnih vrtnji.

ZNAAJKA SUPER PONOVNE VRTNJE ne moe se ne moe pokrenuti u
 ZNAAJCI BESPLATNIH VRTNJI. Simbol         ne postoji na rolama u
 KRUGU BESPLATNIH VRTNJI i znaajka se ne moe ponovno pokrenuti.
SLUAJNOST
Igre sa srednjom razinom sluajnosti imaju stabilne dobitke, a isplate se kreu od malih do vrlo velikih.
PRAVILA IGRE

Svi simboli donose dobitke s lijeva na desno na odabranim dobitnim linijama.
Dobitak iz besplatnih vrtnji dodaje se dobitku s dobitnih linija.
Svi dobici mnoe se s ulogom po liniji.
Sve su vrijednosti prikazane kao stvarni dobici u noviima.
Kada postoje dobici na vie linija, svi se dobici dodaju ukupnom dobitku.
Isplauje se samo najvei dobitak po liniji.
